      %div{:onclick => "console.log('RETRY')", :style => "color: #eeff41;"}  מה זה אומר?
    
    %paper-toast.core-transition.core-transition-bottom{:id => :toast1, :role => "status", :style => "position: fixed; outline: none; display: none;", :tabindex => "-1", :text => "Your draft has been discarded.", "touch-action" => "none"}
